name: treetaggerwrapper
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "treetaggerwrapper" %}
{% set version = "2.3" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/treetaggerwrapper-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8d4a291fef263ee8b546e6368e407e984ba466d5afa56e6ffc2ae495f3414b67

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python =>3
  run:
    - python =>3
    - six

test:
  imports:
    - treetaggerpoll
    - treetaggerwrapper
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip
    - six

about:
  home: https://perso.limsi.fr/pointal/dev:treetaggerwrapper
  summary: Wrapper for the TreeTagger text annotation tool from H.Schmid.
  license: AGPL-3.0-or-later
  license_file: README.txt
  doc_url: http://treetaggerwrapper.readthedocs.org/
  dev_url: https://sourcesup.renater.fr/scm/?group_id=647

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - HeavyTony2
